rst=Adam|date=29 April 2009|ref={{SfnRef|Thomas|2009}}}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.thrashhits.com/2008/07/live-iron-maiden-london-twickenham-stadium-5-july-2008/|title=Iron Maiden live at Twickenham|accessdate=12 October 2008|work=Thrash Hits|date=28 July 2007|ref={{SfnRef|Thrash Hits|2007}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803023522/http://www.thrashhits.com/2008/07/live-iron-maiden-london-twickenham-stadium-5-july-2008/|archive-date=3 August 2008|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}\n* {{cite web |url= http://www.thrashhits.com/2008/06/metal-hammer-golden-gods-2008-winners-and-gossip/ |title= ''Metal Hammer'' awards 2008 winners |date= 17 June 2008 |accessdate= 1 September 2011 |publisher= Thrash Hits |ref= {{SfnRef|Thrash Hits|2008}} |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110821045432/http://www.thrashhits.com/2008/06/metal-hammer-golden-gods-2008-winners-and-gossip/ |archive-date= 21 August 2011 |url-status=dead |df= dmy-all }}\n* {{cite web|last=Thring|first=Oliver|title=Bruce Dickinson: 'Iron Maiden's Bruce Dickinson - a man child in satan's sweet shop'|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news-review/iron-maidens-bruce-dickinson-a-man-child-in-satans-sweet-shop-wcjz6s7wt|website=[[The Sunday Times]]|accessdate=31 October 2017|location=London|date=15 October 2017|ref={{SfnRef|Thring|2017}}}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.ukrockfestivals.com/donington-1988.html|title=Donington \u2013 Iron Maiden|accessdate=12 October 2009|publisher=UK Rock Festivals|ref={{SfnRef|UK Rock Festivals}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.upvenue.com/article/1549-iron-maiden-releases-en-vivo-blu-ray-dvds-and-soundtrack.html |title=Iron Maiden Releasing ''En Vivo!'' Blu-Ray, 2DVD and Soundtrack |date=17 January 2012 |accessdate=17 January 2012 |work=UpVenue|ref={{SfnRef|UpVenue}}}}\n* {{cite episode |title= VH1's 100 Greatest Hard Rock Artists |series= [[The Greatest (TV series)|The Greatest]] |credits= [[Carmen Electra]] (host) |network= [[VH1]] |station= |city= |airdate= 1